    "Section 3 provides the preliminaries related to our research, including the problem definition of federated sequential recommender systems and basic sequential recommender systems.",
    "Then, in Section 4, we present the technical details of our proposed FELLAS, including item-level LLM service and privacy-preserving sequence-level LLM service, followed by two inference attack methods.",
    "The experimental results with comprehensive analysis are exhibited in Section 5.",
    "Finally, Section 6 gives a brief conclusion of this paper and provides some future research directions.",
    "In this section, we present the literature reviews for four related topics: sequential recommendation [49], federated recommendation [42,56,58], contrastive learning in recommendation [59], and LLM as service [11]."
